{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_05_02",
  "title": "小美山愛 2話 単独のお仕事",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後、迷子になった愛達は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few hours later‚ they got lost.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……結局、キャンプ場で一泊することになったのか\nまぁ、野宿されるよりはずっとマシだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ in the end‚ we're going to spend the night at the campsite.\nWell‚ it's much better than sleeping outdoors‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3252187451,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2558.8070472999993,
          "startTime": 8.8840257924
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ご心配をおかけしてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I'm sorry for causing you concern.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2392008107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "愛、来てくれて良かった\n様子が気になってたんだ。困ったことはないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ I'm glad you came.\nI was worried about how things were going. Is everything okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4235538443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 19.9058674773
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　無事テントも借りられましたし\n食材も調達出来ました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! We were able to rent the tent without any problem‚\nand we also got the ingredients!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9313631051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "これから、みんなでカレーを作って食べるところです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're about to cook and eat curry together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.1058674773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 28.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうか\n大変なことになったけど楽しめているみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nIt turned into quite a situation‚ but it looks like you're enjoying it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、こんなに楽しい夏は初めてです！\n今、ワクワクしてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ it's my first summer having so much fun!\nI'm really excited right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "良かった\nじゃあ、莉央さん達に気付かれる前に戻って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's good to hear.\nWell‚ let's go back before Rio-san and the others notice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　また絶対来ますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I'll definitely come back again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3133.333333400003,
          "startTime": 46.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数十分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Tens of minutes later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "愛達の泊まるテントでボヤ騒ぎが起き……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A fire breaks out in the tent……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 51.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……危なかったな。まさかボヤ騒ぎなんて起きるとは\nでも新曲のヒントは掴めたようだし、結果オーライか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That was close. I never expected such a commotion to happen.\nBut it seems like we got some hints for the new song‚ so I guess it's all right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5333.333333300005,
          "startTime": 62.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……夕食、食べ損ねたな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I missed dinner…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2733.33333330001,
          "startTime": 68.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "愛こそお疲れ様。ボヤ騒ぎもあったし大変だったろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ you too. It must have been tough with all the commotion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 77.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、私は平気です！\n……それと、遅くなってすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much‚ but I'm fine!\n…And‚ I'm sorry for being late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 84.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "私達が作ったカレー、持って来ました\n食べていただけますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We made some curry‚ and I brought it.\nWould you like to try it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 89.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ありがたくいただくよ\n……美味い。涙が出るくらい美味い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I gratefully accept.\n…Delicious. It's so good that it brings tears to my eyes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 99
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなに慌てて食べなくても\nくすっ、よっぽどお腹が空いてたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-You don't have to eat so fast…\n*Giggle* It seems like you were really hungry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 105.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……ごちそうさま。今夜は晩飯抜きを覚悟してたんだ\n愛は気遣いが出来るな。大人だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thanks for the meal. I was prepared to skip dinner tonight.\nYou're considerate‚ Ai. You're an adult.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、オーバーですよ\n私なんてまだまだ子供です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ you're exaggerating.\nI'm still far from being an adult.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "昼間だって私\n誰にも相手にされなかったじゃないですか～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even during the day‚\nno one paid any attention to me~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 128.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いや、愛には大人の魅力がある\n外見的にも内面的にもだ。もっと自信を持って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ Ai‚ you have the charm of an adult.\nBoth in appearance and personality. Have more confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 136.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……ビーチでは\n私、誰にも声を掛けてもらえなかったんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-But… At the beach‚\nno one talked to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それは、愛が下を向いて、小さくなっていたからだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's because you were looking down and shrinking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 146.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あれじゃあ、誰からも声なんて掛けられないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that state‚ no one will approach you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "……言われてみたら、そんな風だったかもしれません\n私、カッコ悪い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Now that you mention it‚ maybe I was like that.\nI looked uncool…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 158.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんも葵さんも、それにこころだって\nいつも自信があって堂々としてますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ Aoi-san‚ and even Kokoro…\nThey always have confidence and stand out‚ don't they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "私は……他のみんなが目立っていればいいやって\n自分は別に目立つ必要はないんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it was fine if everyone else stood out\nand I didn't need to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "そう思って、みんなの陰に隠れちゃってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I hid behind everyone's shadow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 180.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……なぁ、愛。そもそも大人ってなんだと思う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ Ai. What do you think being an adult means?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 185.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりません。なんでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I don't know. What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "責任を持つ人のことだ。愛は今LizNoirの\nメンバーとして、責任を持って仕事をしているよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It means taking responsibility. Right now‚ you're working as a\nmember of LizNoir‚ and you're fulfilling your responsibilities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 197.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
