      "text": "ありがとう、ございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you… very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 200.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "でもそれだけじゃない。一人のアイドルとして\n小美山愛として、もっと積極的に活動してみないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that's not all. As an individual idol‚\nas Ai Komiyama‚ why don't you try being more proactive?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "私単独のお仕事をもっと……ってことですか？\nでも、私は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You mean‚ doing more solo work…?\nBut‚ I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 215.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh016.m4a",
