      "text": "わ、私に単独グラビアのお話ですか！？\nなんだか、考える時間があまりなかったですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait‚ are you saying they want to shoot a solo gravure with me!?\nI didn't have much time to think about it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
