        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-ai025.m4a",
      "text": "私みたいな子供、絶対浮いちゃいます\n自信を持って断言出来ます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A shy person like me would definitely stand out.\nI can say with confidence…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや自信って……\nほら、また俯いてるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ have some confidence…\nLook‚ you're looking down again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
